snippet.textDisplay: That Charli kid claims she made up dance moves that are 50+ years old already. If she were up there reciting Shakespeare out of context and out order, mixing lines from 10 different plays...then claiming it as her own....PEOPLE WOULD CALL THAT OUT. Sorry bud she’s not repping dance well at all. She’s just repping herself and using other people’s contributions to maximize her own public image. snippet.textDisplay: Younger voters turn out is likely so low because a lot of young people, myself included, don't really know when/where to vote. A lot of people my age (That I have spoken to) have a hard time following politics because they feel disenfranchised and feel like watching it worsens depression as they see the state of the world. Because of this, a lot of people I have spoken to simply don't follow anything and don't know when/how to vote early or anything like that. I'm not saying that it can't be researched and discovered on your own. However, a lot of people don't even know where to start and are overwhelmed by the prospect of figuring that out and wait for someone to tell them. Sadly, many are not getting that person to tell them when and how to vote in their area. It's sad but I suspect that is a large factor in the voting process now days.

snippet.textDisplay: I think this debate will be extremely telling of Biden's mental state and how capable he is of taking on this election. My expectation is Bernie will mop the floor with him. Also, we can't blame young voters for not showing up when multiple states have closed polling places and forced working, young people to wait in line for HOURS to vote. The average young american worker does not have the time in their day or the money to take off of work to stand in line. The real problem lies in the DNC and the voting process making it hard for working people to cast their vote. Not to mention all of the trump supporters who are going out to vote for Biden purely to try and rig the election in Trumps favor. This is going to be.... an interesting year to say the least.
